805-17 : the man and his maps / by John R. H\u00e9bert. Imago mundi, v. 39, pp. 50-72. 1987. p. 64, no. 22. On left side: Plat 51. LC Luso-Hispanic World, 927 Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:39:14.781Z", "group": ["gmd.mar", "catalog-split-13", "catalog", "general-maps", "main-catalog-split-13"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013585032/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd401/g4013/g4013w/lh000927.gif", "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/gmd/gmd401/g4013/g4013w/lh000927.gif#h=150&w=192", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd401:g4013:g4013w:lh000927/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=588&w=754", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmd401:g4013:g4013w:lh000927/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=1177&w=1509"], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "location": ["washington parish", "united states", "saint tammany parish", "louisiana"], "mime_type": ["image/gif", "image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["sheet", "2013585032", "2014-10-06t13:01:56", "2025-06-07t05:27:39.200000"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map"], "partof": ["cultural landscapes", "geography and map division", "catalog"], "score": 36.226517, "shelf_id": "G4013.W3G46 1805 .M2", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["cadastral maps", "saint tammany parish", "maps", "louisiana", "washington parish (la.)", "saint tammany parish (la.)", "real property", "manuscript maps", "washington parish", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-04-29T16:07:16.015Z", "title": "[Map of an area along Bayou Bogue Chitto, Spanish West Florida]", "type": ["cartographic"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2013585032/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://lccn.loc.gov/2013585036", "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013585036/", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/4b1591b3-563b-5904-acc2-6f1610d99b1e", "htt